headline.print_headline: Australia to Sign Uranium Trade Deal With India
headline.main: Australia to Sign Uranium Trade Deal With India

lead_paragraph: Australia's prime minister said Wednesday that he will sign a uranium export deal with India for peaceful power generation this week, but added that exports of the nuclear fuel to Russia have been banned until further notice.
